data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this gem of a home, located just a short drive to downtown and in the center of the great town of Hixson. This inviting home features real hardwood floors and energy-efficient windows that will brighten your home and save on utility bills. Modern, upgraded appliances make daily living a comfort, and the spacious family room downstairs offers a versatile space for family gatherings, movie nights, additional bedroom or a home gym. A large, fenced-in backyard adds to the appeal, providing endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment. This is the home you've been waiting for - don't miss your chance!
